{"tid":1012892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港豬噢大橋香港口岸警鐘響 廣播要求過千旅客疏散","createTime":"2019-02-08T02:42:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-08T03:44:01.000Z","uid":51620,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4f1e29ca352a62f754905edf90b9ac6e87c6ebad","tid":1012892,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T02:42:13.000Z","msg":"港珠澳大橋香港口岸啟用以來，首次響起警鐘及要求旅客集體疏散。市民表示，今晨9時許在港珠澳大橋香港口岸欲出境往內地時，突然聽到大堂內響起警鐘及閃起紅燈，隨即有人作出廣播，指「（出現）緊急情況&hellip;&hellip;請（各位）跟隨指示離開」，氣氛緊張。<br />\n<br />\n當時在香港口岸內估計有過千人，包括欲離港的市民，以及剛由內地抵港多個內地旅行團團友，眾人都顯得有點錯愕，不知如何是好。讀者陳先生稱當時曾問過多個職員，大多數表示不知發生甚麼事情，只有一名職員指不排除警鐘誤鳴。截至早上10時，現時仍未有廣播解釋發生何事，以及警鐘響起的原因，有旅客對於應否繼續行程離境乘車感到不知所措。"},{"pid":"028d30054513c3ac11d96395a1c4708792364869","tid":1012892,"uid":19712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T02:45:02.000Z","msg":"用唔夠1年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87c8decdc772aee0a533630bfe45b7866a51bb4a","tid":1012892,"uid":77196,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T02:45:57.000Z","msg":"以鄰國人性格冇人踩人已經好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d53701a216f1a7716be9e846168454b5416fd4a","tid":1012892,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T02:47:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79add9171d7e5aac4de6482777802a2dd8db2183","tid":1012892,"uid":19501,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T02:48:39.000Z","msg":"大橋現正進入休克狀態<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"126bbb54e35b7f1e3db1f056809e986b1986b264","tid":1012892,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T02:48:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d40b1ba63960bb8416a8bb2f9de345b75a158eff","tid":1012892,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"